0www.info.gov.hk&d=dMuVdPjJf30Qxtl2jkPsRKGvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=fb0825e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">直到搵到目的地www.info.gov.hk</a>嘅ip為止<br />\n<br />\n支那如果有自己嘅root dns server，就可以將所有支那內嘅嘢射晒去，再俾個唔啱嘅答案你<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://例如明明我打lihkg.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E4%BE%8B%E5%A6%82%E6%98%8E%E6%98%8E%E6%88%91%E6%89%93lihkg.com&d=dMuVdPjJf30Qxtl2jkPsRKGvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=202668b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">例如明明我打lihkg.com</a>，佢就射我去微博，即係可以變成金仔式內聯網，無論如何都射你返支那<br />\n<br />\n至於點解我話其實唔關事，係因為支那本身就可以靠長城同現有嘅root server嘅mirror做手腳<br />\n<br />\n只不過而家更方便"},{"pid":"f0ad2d8fefc345b240b5bf42372a1d12412d1e9b","tid":1773033,"uid":43724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f29204302f4d7fd08165ab18ad63474c386cc060","tid":1773033,"uid":196924,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"94b7dc3d9f77cafa8df63aca49d279655db890f1","tid":1773033,"uid":43724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4df8863cc9e2b70ca1502ce99d1c34527fbc582","tid":1773033,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T07:04:13.000Z","msg":"加強監控掛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T07:13:43.000Z","msg":"可唔可以解釋下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T09:27:55.000Z","msg":"所謂根域名伺服器<br />\n作用就係...<br />\n我唔識講，唯有用例子講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://例如我想去www.info.gov.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E4%BE%8B%E5%A6%82%E6%88%91%E6%83%B3%E5%8E%BBwww.info.gov.hk&d=dMuVdPjJf30Qxtl2jkPsRKGvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=d1bf6266\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">例如我想去www.info.gov.hk</a><br />\n首先就會喺root dns server得到 &ldquo;.hk&rdquo;個DNS server嘅位置<br />\n<a href=\"http://再喺.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%86%8D%E5%96%BA.hk&d=dMuVdPjJf30Qxtl2jkPsRKGvShGfzVnrv2JJWMS0YvQ%3D&h=30f90bcd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">再喺.hk</a>個top